00:00:02,000 --> 00:00:07,000
You have mastered a very powerful tool in NetBeans, the GridBag Customizer.

2
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:13,000
This tool is really a game changer as it really makes the process of designing GUIs very easy.

3
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:17,000
You were introduced to Swing's GridBagLayout.

4
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:22,000
You learned how to move and resize components within the customizer.

5
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:30,000
You learned how to use the layout properties Fill, Weight, Insets, and Anchor.

6
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:37,000
You learned how to insert and delete rows and columns and how to add new components to the design.

7
00:00:37,000 --> 00:00:38,000
And finally, you learned how

8
00:00:38,000 --> 00:59:00,000
to use Sub Containers to more easily control positioning of groups of components.

